    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Oh my goodness! I have only recently discovered that I like cranberries, and this is the first time I&#39;ve actually made cranberry sauce. This version is so delicious! Thank you for sharing the recipe, Molly.</p>
    </div>

      </li><!-- #comment-## -->
  <li id="comment-5326" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
